9
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:06,000
and work out <i>y</i> in terms of <i>x</i> and you get back two solutions, so really, you have two functions of <i>x</i>,
得到<i>y</i>关于<i>x</i>的解 求解这个方程 会得到两个解 因此 实际会得到两个关于<i>x</i>的函数。

